---
import Section from '../ui/Section.astro';
---

<Section id="testimonials" className="bg-stone-50">
  <div class="testimonials-container">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="testimonials-header">
      <h3 class="testimonials-heading animate-on-scroll fade-in-up">
        Príbehy ľudí z našej komunity, ktorých prax zmenila pohľad na život
      </h3>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials Grid -->
    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="testimonial-card animate-on-scroll scale-in stagger-1">
        <div class="quote-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <blockquote class="testimonial-text">
          Po niekoľkých mesiacoch pravidelnej praxe som si všimol, že dokážem pokojnejšie reagovať na stresové situácie. Meditácia mi pomohla nájsť vnútorný pokoj, ktorý som roky hľadal.
        </blockquote>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">M</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <div class="author-name">Miroslav</div>
            <div class="author-meta">Praktizuje 1 rok</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="testimonial-card featured animate-on-scroll scale-in stagger-2">
        <div class="quote-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <blockquote class="testimonial-text">
          Komunita je neuveriteľne podporujúca. Každý štvrtok sa teším na spoločné cvičenie. Prax mi dala nielen nástroje na prácu s vlastnou mysľou, ale aj pocit spolupatričnosti.
        </blockquote>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">K</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <div class="author-name">Katarína</div>
            <div class="author-meta">Praktizuje 3 roky</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="testimonial-card animate-on-scroll scale-in stagger-3">
        <div class="quote-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <blockquote class="testimonial-text">
          Ako začiatočník som mal obavy, či to zvládnem. Ale prístup tu je veľmi priateľský a trpezlivý. Naučil som sa základy a teraz meditácia je súčasť môjho každodenného života.
        </blockquote>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">P</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <div class="author-name">Peter</div>
            <div class="author-meta">Praktizuje 6 mesiacov</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom CTA -->
    <div class="testimonials-cta">
      <p class="cta-text">
        Pripojte sa k našej komunite
      </p>
      <a href="#practice-info" class="cta-button">
        Začať dnes
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>

<style>
  .testimonials-container {
    max-width: 75rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Header */
  .testimonials-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-12);
  }

  .testimonials-heading {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    letter-spacing: var(--letter-spacing-normal);
  }

  /* Grid */
  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .testimonials-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .testimonials-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  /* Testimonial Cards - Smaller */
  .testimonial-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--spacing-6);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-4);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
    position: relative;
  }

  .testimonial-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-border-hover);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .testimonial-card.featured {
    background: var(--color-background-alt);
    border-color: var(--color-border);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .testimonial-card.featured {
      grid-column: span 2;
      grid-row: span 1;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .testimonial-card.featured {
      grid-column: auto;
    }
  }

  /* Quote Icon */
  .quote-icon {
    width: 1.75rem;
    height: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-slate-300);
  }

  .quote-icon svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  /* Testimonial Text */
  .testimonial-text {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-light);
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  /* Author */
  .testimonial-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-3);
    padding-top: var(--spacing-4);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .author-avatar {
    width: 2.25rem;
    height: 2.25rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-slate-700);
    color: white;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .author-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.125rem;
  }

  .author-name {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .author-meta {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-light);
  }

  /* CTA Section - Smaller */
  .testimonials-cta {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--spacing-8) var(--spacing-6);
    background: var(--color-background-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .cta-text {
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: var(--spacing-3) var(--spacing-6);
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
    letter-spacing: var(--letter-spacing-normal);
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: var(--color-primary-light);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  /* Mobile Adjustments */
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .testimonials-container {
      padding: 0 var(--spacing-4);
    }

    .testimonials-header {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-10);
    }

    .testimonials-heading {
      font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
    }

    .testimonials-grid {
      gap: var(--spacing-5);
    }

    .testimonial-card {
      padding: var(--spacing-5);
    }

    .testimonial-text {
      font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
    }

    .testimonials-cta {
      padding: var(--spacing-6) var(--spacing-4);
    }

    .cta-button {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 44px; /* Touch target */
    }
  }

  /* Tablet */
  @media (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1023px) {
    .testimonials-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-6);
    }

    .testimonial-card.featured {
      grid-column: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
